adminai@adminai-VirtualBox:/home$ type Addition
Addition is a function
Addition () 
{ 
    echo "Enter your first number";
    read numberOne;
    echo "Enter your second number";
    read numberTwo;
    ((answer = $numberOne + $numberTwo));
    if (( answer % 2 == 0 )); then
        echo "Your answer $answer is even";
    else
        echo "Your answer $answer is odd";
    fi
}

adminai@adminai-VirtualBox:/home$ Addition
Enter your first number
4
Enter your second number
7
Your answer 11 is odd

